{"tid":1495854,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"選舉事務處籲電子遞表選民查閱登記資料","createTime":"2019-08-22T08:54:20.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-22T09:53:22.000Z","uid":278685,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"e945f5118602800a05e9c21e8d8ed09de5198a06","tid":1495854,"uid":278685,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-22T08:54:20.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www2.hkej.com/instantnews/current/article/2227425/%E9%81%B8%E8%88%89%E4%BA%8B%E5%8B%99%E8%99%95%E7%B1%B2%E9%9B%BB%E5%AD%90%E9%81%9E%E8%A1%A8%E9%81%B8%E6%B0%91%E6%9F%A5%E9%96%B1%E7%99%BB%E8%A8%98%E8%B3%87%E6%96%99\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww2.hkej.com%2Finstantnews%2Fcurrent%2Farticle%2F2227425%2F%25E9%2581%25B8%25E8%2588%2589%25E4%25BA%258B%25E5%258B%2599%25E8%2599%2595%25E7%25B1%25B2%25E9%259B%25BB%25E5%25AD%2590%25E9%2581%259E%25E8%25A1%25A8%25E9%2581%25B8%25E6%25B0%2591%25E6%259F%25A5%25E9%2596%25B1%25E7%2599%25BB%25E8%25A8%2598%25E8%25B3%2587%25E6%2596%2599&d=MOEBQbH5BhSBv0g7AWUGIUngG4XMVyvHznkFIzn%2BcUY%3D&h=a2a3d381\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www2.hkej.com/instantnews/current/article/2227425/%E9%81%B8%E8%88%89%E4%BA%8B%E5%8B%99%E8%99%95%E7%B1%B2%E9%9B%BB%E5%AD%90%E9%81%9E%E8%A1%A8%E9%81%B8%E6%B0%91%E6%9F%A5%E9%96%B1%E7%99%BB%E8%A8%98%E8%B3%87%E6%96%99</a><br />\n<br />\n<strong>選舉事務處籲電子遞表選民查閱登記資料</strong><br />\n <br />\n選舉事務處發言人表示，處方發現其電腦系統曾於6月14日至7月2日期間出現數次技術性問題，導致346宗經由「選舉事務處電子表格上載平台」方式遞交的選民登記申請，未能成功儲存至其數據庫伺服器，以致未獲處理。選舉事務處就事件向受影響巿民致歉。<br />\n<br />\n《2019年臨時選民登記冊》新登記選民人數近38.6萬名。在6月14日至7月2日期間，約有6萬位市民透過「電子表格上載平台」遞交選民登記申請，使用量較平時大幅增加，建議在此段時間透過該方式遞表的市民，盡快登入「選民資料網上查閱系統」查閱他們的最新登記資料。<br />\n<br />\n選舉事務處呼籲，受影響的巿民盡快於本月25日或之前與處方聯絡，以趕及將其資料加入《2019年正式選民登記冊》，從而可以於11月區議會選舉中投票。"},{"pid":"c13b7ca28196bf3b9e1ede0006d4b993a9a6a6a9","tid":1495854,"uid":278685,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-22T09:00:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dda76e62d22a55c6d68cd86be6893537f30e6f0e","tid":1495854,"uid":87735,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-22T09:43:59.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"97e5384f7c64770a1e907f0901f50075de3c7a09","tid":1495854,"uid":83115,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-22T09:52:45.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"789d7dc2f2b11fbcdbc8ac9551a137f67b208423","tid":1495854,"uid":83115,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-22T09:53:22.000Z","msg":"好撚似小學雞 你多人申請吖 我收唔倒喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}